  "_sources_comment": "Frozen BHSA extracts + the derived entity alias table (docs/SOURCE_AND_SCALING.md, docs/COVERAGE.md), generated OFFLINE by extractor/*.py from local BHSA tf/2021 + the wiki BCD, plus the hand-authored coverage-exceptions sign-off ledger. The Concept-Bank + Figure-Registry indices are GLOBAL / canon-wide (registry/concepts.json + figures.json — SC-0037: one code per concept/figure across the whole Bible, so the Facilitator anchors them consistently everywhere), vendored OFFLINE by extractor/build_concept_figure_registry.py from the canon-wide concepts/ + figures/ notes so `tripod id-check` can verify CB_/FIG_ reference-integrity + name-binding. (The per-book CAST — beings/places/objects, the *.aliases.json tables — stays per-book.) All pinned by sha256 so coverage reconciliation + id-check are reproducible. Source extracts: regenerate via the recorded extractor/build commands. coverage-exceptions.json: a governed reviewer sign-off — edits are recorded (SC-ref + provenance) and re-pinned.",
